# The Coal has been successfully inserted into the Stone Furnace, which now has fuel. 
# However, the furnace is still showing a status of "NO_INGREDIENTS," indicating that it does not have any Iron Ore to smelt into Iron Plates.

# I need to insert the Iron Ore into the Stone Furnace so that it can begin the smelting process.
insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, furnace, quantity=10)  # Insert all 10 Iron Ore into the Stone Furnace.
print(f'Inventory after inserting iron ore: {inspect_inventory()}')
print(f'Furnace status {inspect_inventory(furnace)}')  # Check the status of the Stone Furnace again.
